==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: male berry
<hw>male" ber`ry</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A deciduous much-branched shrub
(<spn>Lyonia ligustrina</spn>) with dense downy panicles of small
bell-shaped white flowers; also called <altname>swamp
andromeda</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> privet andromeda, he-huckleberry, <spn>Lyonia
ligustrina</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A kind of coffee. See <er>Pea
berry</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>male body</ent>⟦br⟧
